<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>お知らせ</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .announcement {
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #fff;
            display: flex;
        }

        .announcement-icon {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background-image: url('https://cdn.glitch.global/441c91ae-2a7f-4142-9ffb-ab0c7066dfa1/IMG_1281.png?v=1718682861752');
            background-size: cover;
            margin-right: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .announcement-details {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .announcement h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .announcement .timestamp {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .announcement p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .profile-card {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 10px;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .announcement-icon:hover + .announcement-details .profile-card {
            display: block;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="announcement">
        <div class="announcement-icon"></div>
        <div class="announcement-details">
            <h2>お知らせ</h2>
            <p class="timestamp">投稿時間: 2024年6月18日 12:00</p>
            <p>このお知らせはまだない</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="announcement">
        <div class="announcement-icon"></div>
        <div class="announcement-details">
            <h2>サイト作成</h2>
            <p class="timestamp">投稿時間: 2024年6月18日 13:15</p>
            <p>簡単に再生＆ダウンロード出来るサイトを作成中です...</p>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-card">
            <h3>わかめ02</h3>
            <p>あたままっしろ</p>
        </div>
    </div>


</body>

</html>
